Interface IHidChannel

This is a wrapper for a stream of incoming HidReports from a device and a callback to output HidReports to a device.

Namespace: Jabra.NET.Sdk.Comm
Assembly: Jabra.NET.Sdk.dll
Syntax
public interface IHidChannel
Remarks

Each instance of IHidChannel is associated with only one device, and additionally, only one of its physical/wireless connections to the system.
